<p>3 In reply Evatt referred Curtin to his cablegram E55 (Document 180) and advised that a decision be deferred until he had had a chance to speak to Churchill in Washington. See cablegram E59 of 7 May on file AA:A989, 43-44/715/5/2/2.</p>

